---
---

<section id="manifesto" aria-label="Philosophy">
  <div class="glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="body">
    <p class="s-label rv" style="margin-bottom:2.25rem;">02 — Why now→next</p>
    <blockquote class="manifesto-q rv">
      The gap between <em>now</em> and <em>next</em> is where most companies
      get stuck. Too slow to build. Too rigid to change. Too siloed to align.
      I close that gap — <em>fast, smart, and without the ceremony.</em>
    </blockquote>

    <div class="pillars">
      <div class="rv">
        <p class="pillar-label">Speed</p>
        <p class="pillar-text">
          AI coding teams compress months into weeks. First working version
          in days. Iterate on the spot. Deliver before the market moves.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rv rv-d1">
        <p class="pillar-label">Clarity</p>
        <p class="pillar-text">
          No methodology theater. Clear goals, aligned teams,
          tangible progress visible every sprint —
          from C-suite to the people shipping.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rv rv-d2">
        <p class="pillar-label">Transformation</p>
        <p class="pillar-text">
          Done right, it's metamorphosis. Done wrong,
          you're just a faster caterpillar.
          I've seen both — I do the former.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 10rem 3.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .glow {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201,104,16,.05) 0%, transparent 65%);
  }

  .body { position: relative; max-width: 1000px; }

  .manifesto-q {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 3.2vw, 2.7rem);
    letter-spacing: -.03em;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .manifesto-q em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .pillar-label {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: .6rem;
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: .85rem;
  }

  .pillar-text {
    font-size: .9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    section { padding: 5rem 1.75rem; }
    .pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
